*"On je veoma težak čovek." (He is a very heavy man.)

*"Težak je život." (Life is hard.)

*"Ona je zadužena za težak zadatak." (She is responsible for a difficult task.)

*"Kako je težak kofer?" (How heavy is the suitcase?)

*"Svi znamo da je to težak put." (We all know that it is a difficult journey.)

*"Težači su bili naporni." (The laborers were exhausting.)

*"Težak je čovek koji se nikada ne predaje." (A man is strong who never gives up.)